==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Panhandle
<hw>Pan"han`dle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The handle of a
pan;</def> <specif>hence,</specif> <mark>fig.</mark>, <def>any arm or
projection suggestive of the handle of a pan; <as>as, the
<ex>panhandle</ex> of West Virginia, Texas, or Idaho</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Panhandle State</ent>⟦br⟧

